3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): LDPC codes are commonly used in communication systems, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a method to improve the performance of LDPC decoding, which can be applied in control systems.
